@author Ilya Arefiev (arefiev.id@gmail.com)

This is a java implementation of http://api.myshows.ru/ represented as a library
Read docs for MyshowsClient to know how to use library.

=== BUILDING ===

Run
    ant release
to build library and documentation, placed in "lib-myshows-$version".
"lib-myshows-$version" directory also contains all necessary libraries required
to work properly.

Current implementation of library(in case you have only .jar file) may be found
in .jar file "META_INF/MANIFEST.MF".
Version info also included into 'MyshowsAPI.java' represented as auto-generated
variable updated on every 'ant compile' run.

Run
    ant jar
to build just .jar, placed in "build/jar".

=== REQUIREMENTS ===

Requires
    commons-logging-1.1.1.jar
    httpclient-4.0.1.jar
    httpcore-4.0.1.jar
    org-json.jar
placed near assembled .jar file to work properly.

